Enterprise-level Hybrid Automation Framework developed using Selenium WebDriver, Java, TestNG, Maven, Jenkins, Docker, and Rest Assured for scalable UI and API automation testing.
This framework is designed to support robust, maintainable, and high-performance test automation execution across multiple environments with CI/CD integration.

Key Highlights:
✔ Hybrid Framework Architecture
✔ Page Object Model (POM) Design Pattern
✔ Cross-Browser Testing Support
✔ Parallel Test Execution
✔ API Automation using Rest Assured
✔ Jenkins CI/CD Pipeline Integration
✔ Docker-based Test Execution
✔ Reusable Utility Components
✔ Dynamic XPath Handling
✔ Extent Reporting & Screenshot Capture
✔ Data-Driven Testing Support
✔ Maven Dependency Management
✔ Git & GitHub Version Control Integration
✔ Scalable and Maintainable Framework Design

